This is the source code for: http://express.davglass.com/

You must have git, NodeJS 0.2.4 and npm 0.2.0+ installed

To use it, follow these simple steps:

    git clone git://github.com/davglass/yui-express.git
    cd yui-express
    make npm

For a normal run:
    ./server.js

Visit: http://localhost:3200/

To use Spark2: http://github.com/davglass/spark2

Install spark2 via:

    npm install spark2
    spark2

Visit: http://localhost:3200/
